WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:01.466
What's wrong with me?

2
00:00:02.466 --> 00:00:04.066
Where am I?

3
00:00:04.300 --> 00:00:05.166
You are poisoned

4
00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:06.800
I saved you with elixir

5
00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:09.166
What is poisoning?

6
00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:13.233
Very likely

7
00:00:13.733 --> 00:00:15.900
It was the same person who poisoned it ten years ago

8
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.866
Then why didn't you save me before?

9
00:00:18.866 --> 00:00:21.800
You're going to save me from the grave

10
00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:23.600
Since they want you dead

11
00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:24.733
If you don't die

12
00:00:24.733 --> 00:00:26.133
They will never stop dying

13
00:00:26.133 --> 00:00:27.000
If so

14
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.300
Why don't you die first?

15
00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:30.166
See what works

16
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.066
Are you trying to lead the snake out of the hole?

17
00:00:34.133 --> 00:00:35.200
Yes, Uncle Shen

18
00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:35.900
So

19
00:00:35.900 --> 00:00:38.566
You have to exist as a dead person for a while

20
00:00:38.566 --> 00:00:41.100
It doesn't matter if I can't show up

21
00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:43.066
But I'm just worried about flesh and blood.

22
00:00:43.066 --> 00:00:46.200
He's all alone now.

23
00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.566
I'll take care of him for you.

24
00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:51.766
Where am I going now?

25
00:00:51.866 --> 00:00:53.833
Don't worry, I have my own arrangements.

26
00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.400
Every time I see you, it's my own

27
00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:02.200
Don't be so polite.

28
00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:03.366
Whatever you want

29
00:01:03.366 --> 00:01:05.700
It was Mr. Shen who lived with you first

30
00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:07.466
The safety issue is up to you

31
00:01:07.466 --> 00:01:09.800
I will definitely take good care of Mr. Shen

32
00:01:15.566 --> 00:01:18.566
Remember to arrange a shareholder attack tomorrow

33
00:01:18.566 --> 00:01:21.100
You must get it from Shen Xuerou

34
00:01:21.100 --> 00:01:24.100
The control of Longshan Group is in your hands

